*po͝os'i, /ˈpʊsi/, /<tt>"pUsi</tt>/

====Noun====
{{en-noun-reg-y|puss|y}}

# (''informal; also'' '''pussy-cat''') An affectionate term for a [[cat]].
# (''taboo slang'') The female [[genitalia]].
# (''informal'') A [[coward]].

